SAR Plugin for OpenCPN
======================

The purpose of this plugin is to provide Search and Rescue Patterns (SAR) plotting capability to OpenCPN.

The aims are to:

1. Generate GPX files for a number of SAR patterns
2. Plot selected SAR patterns directly in OpenCPN

Building
========

The plugin uses a continous integration setup described in the
[wiki](https://github.com/Rasbats/managed_plugins/wiki/Alternative-Workflow)
This setup is also able to push all updated metadata files to a clone
of https://github.com/OpenCPN/plugins in order to simplify pull requests
against this site.

Pull Requests
=============
Please make any pull requests against these two repositories:
https://github.com/Rasbats/sar_pi (Maintainer)
https://github.com/SaltyPaws/SAR_pi (Original Source)

